### Para recuperar información sobre el Pokémon "Ditto"
GET http://localhost:1234/pokemon/ditto
###
GET http://localhost:1234/

### Para crear un nuevo pokemon
POST http://localhost:1234/pokemon
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Pikachu nuevo",
    "type": "Electric",
    "moves": [
        "transform"
    ]
}

### URL no existente
GET http://localhost:1234/pokemon/unknown